        <div xml:id="TK141">
            <lg type="edition">
<l>piṟaṉporuḷāṭ peṭṭuoḻukum pētaimai ñālat </l>
<l>taṟamporuḷ kaṇṭārka ṇil</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>The folly of desiring her who is the property of another will not be found in those who know (the attributes of) virtue and (the rights of) property.</l>
            </lg>
